Package models

Class Prescription

java.lang.Object
models.Prescription
public class Prescription extends Object
The Prescription class represents a medical prescription issued by a doctor to a patient. It contains details about the prescribing doctor, patient, prescribed medication, issuance date, and expiry date.

    • Prescription

      public Prescription(String prescID, Doctor doctor, Patient patient, Medication medication, LocalDate prescDate)
      Constructs a new Prescription object. The expiry date is automatically set to one year from the prescription date.
      Parameters:
      prescID - The unique ID of the prescription.
      doctor - The doctor who issued the prescription.
      patient - The patient receiving the prescription.
      medication - The medication prescribed.
      prescDate - The date the prescription was issued.
